OL,5, The sister of a head teacher who took  
OL,6, her own life after an Ofsted inspection
OL,7, has criticised the watchdog's boss for 
OL,8, defending it.                          
OL,10,FAmanda Spielman told the BBC she had no
OL,11,Freason to doubt the report into        
OL,12,FCaversham Primary in Reading.          
OL,14,FHead teacher Ruth Perry died in        
OL,15,FJanuary, knowing inspectors would      
OL,16,Fdowngrade the school's rating.         
OL,18,FHer sister, Prof Julia Waters, said Ms 
OL,19,FSpielman's response was "totally       
OL,20,Finadequate".                           
